Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ED2 ENG
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ED2 KARAOKE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.63,Background2,,0,0,0,,...number 49 bound for Nishi-Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.61,Note,,0,0,0,,Nationwide Railway Timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I catch up to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I do catch up to her, what the heck do I say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have the right to stop Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, are you going sightseeing, at this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pitch-dark; you won't be able to see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I'm meeting a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,On that promontory?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Son, you're not by any chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the construction's done, so I guess there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.05,Note,,0,0,0,,Tip of the Promontory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:35.65,Note,,0,0,0,,You have only that one life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:37.86,Note,,0,0,0,,Don't throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I pass her up somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else... she couldn't have already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what train Misaki took from the timetable she left in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I shelled out for a limited express train to chase her; there's no way I'm not in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.38,Note,,0,0,0,,If you have the courage to jump, have the courage to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I overconfident in guessing she'd come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Misaki, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The time you arrived was only five minutes apart from when I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You could become a detective, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do because you weren't saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go home? It's cold here and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.91,Note,,0,0,0,,If you have the courage to jump, have the courage to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't die! Let's live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no joke! Thanks to you, the money I worked so hard for is blown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been better if I'd died yesterday as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like my stepfather said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm around, everybody meets with misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother dying was also my fault. My original father dying probably was too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My stepfather tried his hardest to get rid of me, but he failed and, predictably, his luck went bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I started helping my aunt, her recruiting stopped going well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and she started fighting a lot with my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All of that was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a worthless human being who summons misfortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a person this world doesn't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't want to admit that. That's why I planned your project.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If just one single person needed me, my stepfather's words would have been proven wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be okay for me to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But that project ended in failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not needed even by you, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in my being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you pulled that "New Year's grated yams" crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That stunt was just like saying, "Come after me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, when I saw you just now, I thought my heart was going to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been fine if it had stopped though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, you know, a final note is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no note, it's trouble for the people you leave behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,not knowing whether it was a suicide or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what happened with my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give this up. I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be good things too, if you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle and your aunt and such would grieve!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you... That's it, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you! I love you! Please, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You say funny things, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I am going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's useless after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any words to hold Misaki back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, what's wrong with her dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the same. The only difference is whether it happens early or late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like Misaki said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even to live into the future will just mean misery, with nothing but painful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Being alive is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dying is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't, absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go saying you're going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My imagination is poor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can't make myself believe in God as well as other people do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All he would have to do is cause a really flashy miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,like in the Bible or something, right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And if only I could believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I could blame all the bad things on God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, not even a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are others who are to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Others who have made you suffer, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Where lies the reason why Misaki suffers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If Misaki is always hurting and lonely, so that she can't go on, that's an abomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it means there exists a source of that evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone evil who's making Misaki suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know something? There are conspiracies in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But ninety-nine percent of all so-called "conspiracies" are simply imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or they're just big lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, one percent of it is the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody has, against extreme odds, become aware of a genuine conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Tatsuhiro Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And the enemy's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known the name since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The evil organization that makes us suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, their name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The N.H.K.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,N.H.K.?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Their name is the N.H.K.,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a secret society that covers all the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The misfortune that occurs around you is all the work of the N.H.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, what are you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mental assault from the N.H.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told the organization's secret to you, Misaki, so they've come to do away with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What is this N.H.K.?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japan Social-Withdrawal Association!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The evil secret society that turned me into a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the Japan Frailty Association!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They went after Senpai's frail heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and drove her to participate in the offline meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The wicked hand of an N.H.K. is also reaching for you, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That one is the Japan Pessimism Association!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them and only them who have driven you, Misaki, into thinking negatively about everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All the misfortunes that happen in the world are conspiracies by the N.H.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not your fault, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like the name N.H.K., call it whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,God, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,God?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's come at last to finish me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see him too, can't you, Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can! Focus your eyes well and look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! I can't see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can! I'm absolutely sure you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the source of all evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The last boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't go without a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dragging him down with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the one and only item that can defeat him:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Revolution Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Using this is the only way to defeat that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way is to throw myself into a kamikaze attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll guard your life, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything up till now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Live in good health in the future! And lead a happy life for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my final request!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Misaki, live on for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that this kind of thing is the only way that comes to mind to secure the life of a girl I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot, truly an idiot. Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"A girl I like?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What, then? I actually was in love with Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A dramatic death just isn't fitting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to die for Misaki, the girl I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ultimate in "dramatic," don't you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...the construction's done...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Construction"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the construction's done, so I guess there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they intend to keep me from dying dramatically at any price?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look! What are you crying about? I'm the one who feels like crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If it took almost an hour by taxi, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If we walk to the station, it will take till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.04,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H625E52&\3c&HFFFFF2&\bord5\shad0\fscx149.813\fscy147.5\pos(626.666,487.5)\frz348.471\an2}No Signal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as things stand, in the end we're gonna freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an abandoned house nearby though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,An abandoned house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's the house my original father built.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave me my name too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Because Ishihama Misaki promontory is nearby," he said. Pretty random, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This was my room. I was using it until my third year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first person outside my family who's ever come in here, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:17:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my stepfather got angry if I brought friends home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warmer this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you tell me something about yourself too, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll listen, no matter how boring it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll tell about a dream I had this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A jet-black snake came out of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and started blasting away with a gun glowing with black light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then with a long, thick sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The penalty for sexual harassment is a million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then should I talk about my childhood or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I was a kid, I used to play baseball and stuff a lot at a park near my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you'd call it baseball, what with using a rubber ball and a plastic bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, it's possible I'll be getting married in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I came back here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,my parents have been bugging me to have arranged marriage meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I do? So, just once I met someone, for their sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I unexpectedly hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently she liked me too, and by now we're nuts about each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, are you keeping healthy in your hikikomori state?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My baby was born without incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our home is a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is moving forward under full sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable, everybody I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't wanna go! What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't! I can't, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, make the best of things, all you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to get along too, however I can, to keep hanging in there the best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your patronage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.62,Note,,0,0,0,,Beware of Molesters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late! How many times have I said, "Come right away after you eat dinner."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I did just finish dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And are you in some elevated position to order me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that my aunt and uncle feel at ease while I'm spending time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what about the homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's humiliating, somehow, to be learning subjects from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped out of high school. I dropped out of college.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody could see which of us is the more accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'm gonna pass the test to enter a better college than you went to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of what it is, my N.H.K.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By means of your actions, the evil god has perished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't be sure that evil won't ever revive itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That being the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Japan Hostage Exchange Association?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Each member offers their life as a hostage to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, it says "If you die, I'll die too, you scoundrel!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do that, just like the faceoff between nuclear powers during the Cold War,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,even if one wants to die, they won't be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,not a single one of our problems has been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, too, we'll probably be whispering "I can't, I can't" every day while we go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But still... Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how long it will hold up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll give it a try as best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:21:59.79,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Tatsuhiro Sato\NMisaki Nakahara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I'm sure both you and I will be okay, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the N.H.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:14.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,136.135)\fs60.504\c&H6EB3FF&}Final Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:14.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H459DFF&\pos(640,468.907)\fs60.504}Welcome to the N.H.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.35,0:22:32.27,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}Even if this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:36.86,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}were to end tomorrow, since it's you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:40.82,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}would you take the curt attitude of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.36,0:22:45.70,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}"If so, that's okay with me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:49.66,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}There's no need to strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:54.92,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}Just sometimes would be fine, so lift up your face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:57.92,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}and look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:01.44,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:04.97,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}Though it's a tiny world,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:10.08,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}for some reason it's too big for these two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:13.69,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}Though it's an endless world,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:18.23,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}for some reason it's too small for these two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:20.84,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:25.28,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}in the brilliant morning light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:31.21,ED2_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)}{\blur0.756}I want to laugh with you.
